data.description: Welcome home to this wonderfully updated single family home that is perfectly situated in North Clearwater.  This 3-bedroom, 2-bath gem has been well cared for and is ready for new owners! As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by an open-concept living space that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The interior has been thoughtfully updated, with all hard-surface flooring and a neutral color palette.  The updated kitchen features new appliances and ample counter and cabinet space. The primary bedroom boasts a private en-suite bathroom for added convenience, and both bathrooms have been updated with tile, vanities and fixtures.  The converted garage space is a versatile addition to this property.  Currently set up as the third bedroom with separate indoor laundry, it is the perfect space for a home office, gym, or additional living area to suit your lifestyle. This bonus room adds valuable square footage and endless possibilities, but if you prefer a garage, it can easily be converted back! Step outside into your LARGE, fenced-in backyard with a concrete sitting area perfect for relaxing by the fire pit. Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, this home provides a peaceful retreat while being conveniently located near schools, parks, shopping, and dining.  Located less than 2 miles from downtown Dunedin, and less than 6 miles to both Clearwater Beach and Honeymoon island, you won't want to miss the opportunity to make this your new home!
